## Your Actual Day Now
```
Morning:
  ctx_budget                        ← you call this once
  ctx_tasks()                       ← you call this once
  "start working on shared types"   ← you say this

Claude Code handles everything else:
  ctx_start("shared types")         ← automatic
  [builds]
  ctx_progress(pct: 25, done: [...]) ← automatic
  [builds more]
  ctx_progress(pct: 100, done: [...]) ← automatic
  "shared types done. Start dynamo-client?"

  ctx_start("dynamo-client")        ← automatic
  [builds]
  ...

End of day:
  close terminal                    ← auto-checkpoint fires
```

You call three commands all day. Claude Code does the rest.

